Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through. Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you were going to die alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's heartbreaking, Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see people\Nsacrificing themselves anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Parting Builds a Man's Character!\NSanji and Chopper"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that leg, you won't\Nbe able to be a pirate any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had the same dream as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... even your men said it doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does! When the\Ntime comes, head to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue surely exists there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, I can't be a pirate anymore,\Nbut this time, you can go and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Geezer, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:04:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just do as you please\Nand die as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn geezer gave up\Nhis leg so that I could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't repay the damn geezer for his\Nkindness unless I risk my life for him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying isn't something you\Nshould do to repay kindness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what he saved you for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being given life and yet dying...\Nis something that a weakling would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is there any other way\Nto settle this matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I'm not quite done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me angry.\NI won't let you die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That bastard Krieg brings\Nout weapons one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that chore boy can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if hundreds of weapons are built in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can be defeated by someone\Nwith a spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a pirate battle, if you fear death\Nfor even a moment, you'll fall to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that kid doesn't have any hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a survival instinct...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he not fear death\Nbecause he has faith in himself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet Krieg gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hundreds of weapons and poison...\NIf they're all force...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then that kid's spear is also force...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spear held in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know an idiot who's holding back\Nthat spear for a stupid reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna end it... for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Gavel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve my goal, the All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll come along... on your journey\Nto become "King of the Pirates"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the cook for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!! All right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! Yaay! We got a cook!\NWe'll have good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you all sorts of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I don't like it! I wanted to\Nkick you out from here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you decide it so easily...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you resort to bad acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear everything, since you're all stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to say, you're willing to go that far\Nto kick me out, huh, you damn geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to\Ntalk like that?! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! That's right, little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like kids to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single day passed where I didn't regret\Nletting a useless one live, you damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Fine by me, you damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the rest of your life to the utmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is a nice ship.\NIs it okay for us to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It's Sanji's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner Zeff!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the damn things\Nyou've done for me over all these years!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget your kindness...\Nfor the rest of my life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sad, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men should part without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!! Set sail!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you again, you damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't fear even death\Nbecause you have faith in yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll find the All Blue... for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Customers are gonna show up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:13:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin has been alone all this time...\Njust like I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been shot? We need to stop\Nthe bleeding right away or you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can! You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can! You can be a great doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doct... I can't breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you have such a kind heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Robin didn't\Nhave anyone like Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there are some strange\Ncreatures in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really have spent your\Nwhole life disliked by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor monster. Why's a loner\Nlike you trying to save this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Even if I don't\Nhave friends, I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Doctor's flag exists, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's be pirates together! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is, since it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a reindeer! I have antlers and hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even have a blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true... that I wanna be a pirate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even a human! I'm a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become your friend! So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just came to say thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for asking me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one day... if you feel like it, stop by agai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't ask people to join you\Nby telling them to "shut up."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt good! Hey, do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! We're setting sail right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought I'd die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sanji-san! You came to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! It wasn't just a fantasy, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your research was completed then, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was that a lie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Chopper! My research succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lie because I'd be sad\Nif you died without saying so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nothing is impossible for the man\Nwho raised a flag with a skull!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say it again, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, young men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, Ma'am!\N--Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kureha. This dust is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha! What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha! We shot all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make cherry blossoms bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my invention is complete,\Nthis country will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. This red dust isn't ordinary dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will attach to the white snow in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make vivid pink snow fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Hiriluk! I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony Tony Chopper. That's a cool name,\Nisn't it? That's what I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, you'll be able to become\Na good doctor. I'll guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I disappear, my dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had... such a good life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have a safe trip, my stupid son...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore, got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rescue you for sure, so just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruthless Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm bored.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.11,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moai"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moai"\N"[Bored]"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some meat or I'm\Ngonna frickin' kill youse guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:43.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Luffione, Luffione Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I smoke cigars, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz the air in this frickin'\Nworld stinks, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,(Dandy)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called youse guys here today for one reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time we made clear who's\Nboss of this town once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, any idiot would realize it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Zorocia, Zorocia Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Sanjino, Sanjino Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanjino, a bonehead like you who\Ndoesn't even slick his hair back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't even qualified to be boss of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my reasons, okay?!\NIt's slicked back on one side, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One side?! Don't make me laugh! That's like\Nsaying you've got half a pair of balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--That's the last straw! This calls for all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you starting the war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, war it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him eat lead, Usotooya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imma gonna take out Zorocia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotooya failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:38.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usotooya of the Luffione Family died in battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take out Luffione while he\Ndon't have his men to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take out Luffione.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopalini failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:49.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chopalini of the Sanjino Family died in battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your enemy well, Namimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take out Sanjino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamma mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:56.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sanjino Family has been taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:22:00.11,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Sanjino of the Sanjino Family\Nascended to heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where's his safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! He sure was loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:06.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Namimore failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:10.70,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Namimore of the Zorocia Family\Ndied from happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. She still killed Sanjino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robita, go take out Luffione.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not interested.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorocia has been betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:25.30,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Zorocia of the Zorocia Family\Ndied thinking, 'I never thought\Nmy ally would kill me.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:26.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They actually shot each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Robita of the Zorocia Family died thinking,\N'It wasn't supposed to be like this.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:32.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Robita failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, I'm the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can stuff myself with as\Nmuch meat as I want in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that meat tastes\Nterrible when I eat it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I finally realized just now\Nwhat the most important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel lonely... I feel lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a dream, I wanna wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that was a dream.\N--Who the hell are you?! And that was a dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with them,\Nthe more I make them suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet friends who will protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything Is for Her Friends!\NRobin in the Darkness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
